==Race and ethnicity==
The ''[[sociology of race and ethnic relations]]'' is the study of [[social]], [[political]], and [[economic]] relations between [[Race (classification of human beings)|races]] and [[ethnicities]] at all levels of society. It encompasses [[racism]] and [[residential segregation]]. 
